{"tid":1179238,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"「找到名字了，真好！」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-05-31T03:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T03:52:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb49643a467eedec6805610cea2d1e0b23b709d9","tid":1179238,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190531/20691491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190531%2F20691491&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoL0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=753d4cf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190531%2F20691491&h=fe921721\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190531/20691491</a><br />\n<br />\n「找到名字了，真好！」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190531/large/e8804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190531%2Flarge%2Fe8804a.jpg&h=79ac9731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n晚上我們吃自助餐。鄰桌都是年輕人，某人生日，同事相約慶祝，十分熱鬧。席間人人滑手機，男男女女都在找──<br />\n<br />\n「找到了！找到了！」<br />\n<br />\n「我母校都有，真好！」<br />\n<br />\n「按連結加名啦，記着校友要列畢業年份。」<br />\n<br />\n「點解我母校排咁後？一定係好遲聯署，激死！」<br />\n<br />\n──原來這批年輕人在全港逾300間大、中學校友師生聯署，反對港府強推《逃犯條例》送中惡法名單中，尋找母校的名字，又回到青葱日子&hellip;&hellip;而此時此刻，校友們隔着空氣心意相通，團結就是力量。<br />\n<br />\n「如果你是7 7 7的師妹點算好？真係陀衰家！」<br />\n<br />\n「趕佢出校友會，再趕佢下台！」<br />\n<br />\n笑死──但7 7 7應該很久沒真心笑過了，只剩冷笑、假笑、奸笑、鄙笑、皮笑肉不笑。港大民研，6成港人不支持她當特首。一向囂張傲慢的林鄭，已用「不屑」來掩飾「恐慌」了，不辯論不解說不商議不聽取建議忠告不理民意世情&hellip;&hellip;發覺她眼神、情緒、表現都有精神病徵兆嗎？泛民請外國介入是「教人點樣對付我」？不但有妄想症，還把自己放大積極邀功。事實上已被阿爺之鷹犬架空，一葉知秋，點都要病一病，藉此下台吧，作孽太多，收尾幾年要好生休養。<br />\n<br />\n散Band了，年輕人們相約：「6 9見！」  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美國傳媒不愛國 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n誰是黑社會 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"0f2acb74a318bba2355cc4b16a56e2c0210d18b7","tid":1179238,"uid":195169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:43:51.000Z","msg":"李碧華真係香港唯一才女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa57f1dd9c57d7b96177d5417b969d6b9d752ee","tid":1179238,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f2acb74a318bba2355cc4b16a56e2c0210d18b7","tid":1179238,"uid":195169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:43:51.000Z","msg":"李碧華真係香港唯一才女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37053ab801cca3933285a440da8a4fc3634cb739","tid":1179238,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:51:36.000Z","msg":"精神病徵兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n形容得好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40dbfe50c1a8c521bb5b9b5af3b77650f0493d0","tid":1179238,"uid":178459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}